<node id="&quot;ARBIN INSTRUMENTS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORGANIZATION"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Arbin Instruments is a company specializing in advanced battery testing technologies, providing innovative solutions for battery performance evaluation and development."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin Instruments is a company specializing in battery testing systems and technologies, known for their LBT Series and advanced testing solutions that enhance the accuracy and precision of battery performance evaluations."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin Instruments is a company that develops testing solutions for battery materials, specifically known for its Three-Electrode Coincell Test Solution."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin Instruments is a company that has established itself as a leader in the battery and energy storage testing industry, focusing on customer relationships and innovative products."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin Instruments is a company that specializes in battery testing solutions and participates in multiple events globally to showcase its products and services."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin Instruments is a company that specializes in battery testing systems and has published various documents on battery test system accuracy and calibration."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin Instruments is a company that specializes in battery testing systems and is mentioned in relation to the accuracy and calibration of their products."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin Instruments is a company that specializes in battery testing systems and provides resources such as manuals and white papers on battery test system accuracy and calibration."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin Instruments is a company with nearly 35 years of experience in high-precision battery testing systems, supporting the ICNaB 2025 conference and promoting innovation in the battery industry."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin Instruments is a leader in battery testing instrumentation with over thirty years of experience, providing high current battery testing systems to support the development of advanced battery technologies."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin Instruments is a leading global supplier of testing instrumentation for energy storage applications, founded in 1991 by Dr. John Zhang."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin Instruments is a company that specializes in high-precision battery test equipment for researchers and the battery industry, offering solutions for various testing applications."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin Instruments is a company that specializes in high-precision battery testing systems and intelligent software solutions aimed at enhancing energy efficiency and supporting R&amp;D breakthroughs in battery technology."</data>
