  <data key="d1">"Arbin is a company specializing in battery testing equipment, known for its innovative solutions that ensure precision in battery research and development."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin is a company that produces high-quality battery test equipment, known for its reliability and precision in the testing process."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin is a company that provides battery rack solutions to enhance laboratory safety and efficiency in battery testing."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin is a company that provides battery testing technology and equipment, supporting research in the field of battery development."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin is a company that provides resources and information regarding battery materials and technologies, as indicated by the source URL."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin is a company that specializes in battery testing equipment, particularly known for its Regenerative Battery Testing (RBT) series designed for high-power applications."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin is a company that specializes in battery testing solutions, providing advanced technology and methodologies for evaluating battery performance and lifespan."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin is a company that develops software for controlling battery testers, including the MITS software which utilizes User-Defined Meta Variables (MV_UD)."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin is a company that provides battery testing solutions, utilizing CAN Bus communication to enhance testing capabilities and safety."&lt;SEP&gt;"Arbin is an organization that specializes in battery testing solutions, including the development of the CAN Bus communication protocol for BMS."</data>
  <data key="d2">chunk-9d5850a3a2de372ceb52706f0a18916f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-135f84a4a69cd7ee2d331daee6ce476d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6621a05c09d802fb067002157ecd76d1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1c23b6ffa21e637142f36af12cf512fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c65340fe2e92691da19cd5df3f81ed19&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d88ddcdef3fbdbd6e832d10dc55189df&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-710c1a7eca22ff32ac802ba9002c83ed&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-de25136c91d61e4f8f26c659fa5af907&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c3f0087a83b08f79d66067b6c207c63b</data>
