  <data key="d2">chunk-6621a05c09d802fb067002157ecd76d1</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;MV_UD3&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"NORMAL_ENTITY"</data>
  <data key="d1">"MV_UD3 is a user-defined meta variable used in Arbin software to store and update values related to battery testing, particularly charge capacity."</data>
